00:06:45.420 --> 00:06:50.900
 - It relates to the general idea

00:06:50.900 --> 00:06:55.900
 of integrity of tissue and cells.

00:06:55.900 --> 00:07:00.460
 And when something goes wrong with a tissue,

00:07:00.460 --> 00:07:04.460
 an energy failure, for example,

00:07:05.380 --> 00:07:10.380
 any tissue loses its barrier function or integrity

00:07:10.380 --> 00:07:15.140
 and things that are inside leak out,

00:07:15.140 --> 00:07:17.860
 things that are outside can get in.

00:07:17.860 --> 00:07:22.860
