00:07:22.860 --> 00:07:29.340
 of fatty material and proteins,

00:07:29.340 --> 00:07:34.340
 but every cell, when it's in a highly energized state,

00:07:35.060 --> 00:07:40.060
 the whole cytoplasm has a fat loving property,

00:07:40.060 --> 00:07:43.380
 a hydrophobic property.

00:07:43.380 --> 00:07:50.140
 The idea of a membrane barrier on the surface of a cell

00:07:50.140 --> 00:07:57.620
 is really a myth.

00:07:57.620 --> 00:08:02.620
 Gilbert Ling spent 40, 50 years disproving that myth.

00:08:03.620 --> 00:08:08.300
 That it's really the structure of the cytoplasm

00:08:08.300 --> 00:08:11.540
 that creates a barrier between any cells

00:08:11.540 --> 00:08:13.180
 inside and that's outside.

00:08:13.180 --> 00:08:18.980
 And Russian researchers in the middle of the last century

00:08:18.980 --> 00:08:23.460
 showed that the energy level of the cell

00:08:23.460 --> 00:08:26.980
 is what governs its barrier function.

00:08:26.980 --> 00:08:31.980
 A high energy state, the cell has a lipid loving quality.

00:08:32.620 --> 00:08:34.820
 Takes up fat easily.

00:08:34.820 --> 00:08:37.060
