00:10:18.140 --> 00:10:20.780
 travel on the albumin.

00:10:20.780 --> 00:10:22.900
 And when you're under stress,

00:10:22.900 --> 00:10:27.900
 the increased free fatty acids will displace those hormones.

00:10:27.900 --> 00:10:34.300
 And the albumin delivers large amounts of free fatty acids

00:10:34.300 --> 00:10:43.660
 or fat soluble hormones to the capillaries

00:10:43.660 --> 00:10:48.080
 serving the brain.

00:10:49.180 --> 00:10:54.180
